title: Shades Of Scarlet 2: Higher Power (Zero Tolerance) 2015 (Split-S
description:
Shades Of Scarlet 2: Higher Power (Zero Tolerance) 2015 (Split-Scenes)

Kendra Lust, Karlie Montana, Abella Danger, Jasmine Jae, Derrick Pierce, Tommy Pistol, Marcus London

... the story continues. A small town reporter played by Kendra Lust is researching the mysterious death of erotic author Roz Collings in hopes of getting her big break. She could never have anticipated where the search for the story would lead her as she descends into a world of sexual insanity. Unsure of whether she is following the story or becoming a part of it, she risks her marriage and her life to get to the truth.

Runtime: 121 minutes
